data.description: OPEN HOUSE Monday, 4-7. Welcome to a cozy oasis at 6822 Sabine Pass! You will be delighted in the roominess in this 2 bed and 2 bath home with a vaulted living room.  The cook will enjoy plenty of cabinets, solid counters, dining nook and a stainless steel refrigerator that conveys. This home is practical with the ceremic tile providing both durability and elegance throughout the home, with only carpet in the primary bedroom. As you step outside onto the deck, you will be surrounded by the shaded trees and space that is perfect for morning coffees or evening stargazing. Close to Lackland AFB, highways and retail. This home is well maintained, water softner and newer HVAC. Make an appointment today!
